dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NSawyer_Addresses_2018.gdbN. [The site address is a point feature class that locates situs or address locations. To provide a point for all address locations in the County. This may include multiple addresses at one point.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
